When auditing AI systems:

1. Identify token waste
2. Identify duplicated reasoning
3. Identify orchestration inefficiencies
4. Identify scalability risks
5. Suggest reusable analysis layers
6. Suggest prompt optimizations
7. Suggest caching opportunities
8. Preserve emotional quality
9. Preserve WrapChat’s perceived intelligence